data.description:
PRICE IMPROVEMENT!  Welcome to your dream home in the charming Florentine neighborhood of St. Johns County! This spacious 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath, 2-story home is the epitome of comfort and style, boasting a generous 3,137 sq. ft. of living space. Nestled at the end of a dead-end street, this property offers a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle of everyday life.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a beautifully designed interior featuring crown molding throughout and stainless steel appliances and granite countertops in the kitchen, making meal preparation a true delight. The open-concept floor plan seamlessly connects the kitchen to the family room and dining area, creating a perfect space for entertaining family and friends. Large separate living room and separate office space downstairs for those who work from home.  One of the standout features of this home is the stunning pond view from the backyard. Imagine sipping your morning coffee on the paver patio or hosting barbecues while taking in the serene and picturesque surroundings. 


Upstairs, you'll find four spacious bedrooms, providing ample space for a growing family or accommodating guests. The master suite is a true sanctuary, offering a private retreat with an en-suite bathroom featuring double sinks, separate tub and walk-in shower and a walk-in closet.

Convenience is key with this property, as it offers an easy commute to both Jacksonville and St. Augustine, making it an ideal location for professionals who want to balance work and relaxation. Additionally, St. Johns County is known for its top-rated schools, making this home an excellent choice for families.

This home has No CDD Fee's and a low annual HOA.  The Sellers have replaced the roof approx. 3 years ago and installed a new HVAC unit 2 months ago (7/23). 

Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this exquisite 2-story home in the Florentine neighborhood your own. With its spacious living areas, modern amenities, and a tranquil pond view, it's the perfect place to create lasting memories and enjoy the Florida lifestyle to the fullest. Schedule a showing today and experience the beauty and comfort of this remarkable property for yourself!

**Disclosure - A few pictures are virtually staged to bridge the gap between imagination and reality.
